  m_text: "Credits \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nA Game by Lost Sheep (Team 4) \r\n\r\nCreated
    for Game Jam Universitar 2026 \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nTeam 4 Members \r\n\r\nIordache
    Cristiana \r\n\r\n\u0218erban Adrian-Gheorghe \r\n\r\nBug\u0103rin Florin-Adrian
    \r\n\r\nIoana-Flavia Bolbotina \r\n\r\nOlosutean Martina-Ioana \r\n\r\nMatca\u0219u
    Miriam-M\u0103lina \r\n\r\nB\xE2lc \u0218tefan Vlad \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nArt Team
    \r\n\r\nB\xE2lc \u0218tefan Vlad \r\n\r\nIordache Cristiana \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nCharacter
    Design  \r\n\r\nB\xE2lc \u0218tefan Vlad \r\n\r\nIordache Cristiana \r\n\r\n
    \r\n\r\nUI \r\n\r\nIordache Cristiana \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nBackgrounds \r\n\r\nB\xE2lc
    \u0218tefan Vlad \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nCharacter Animation \r\n\r\nB\xE2lc \u0218tefan
    Vlad \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nCutscenes \r\n\r\nB\xE2lc \u0218tefan Vlad \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nDesign
    Team \r\n\r\nOlosutean Martina-Ioana \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nProgramming Team \r\n\r\n\u0218erban
    Adrian-Gheorghe \r\n\r\nIoana-Flavia Bolbotina \r\n\r\nBug\u0103rin Florin-Adrian
    \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nMovement, Interaction, Level Flow \r\n\r\n\u0218erban Adrian-Gheorghe
    \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nPlayer System, Level System, Game Manager \r\n\r\nBug\u0103rin
    Florin-Adrian \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nMushroom System, Hints, Visual Effects \r\n\r\nIoana-Flavia
    Bolbotina \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nStorytelling \r\n\r\nMatca\u0219u Miriam-M\u0103lina
    \r\n\r\nOlosutean Martina-Ioana \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nAudio Team \r\n\r\nMatca\u0219u
    Miriam-M\u0103lina \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nTools \r\n\r\nGame made in Unity 6.000.4.2f1
    \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nMusic Credits \r\n\r\n(can also be found in Audio Resources.txt
    file) \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nAudio name:  dogbark.wav   \r\n\r\nSource:https://freesound.org/people/crazymonke9/sounds/418108/ 
